name: Pearls & Lace Baby or Bridal Shower Invitations - Custom
description:
I love the vintage feel of these handmade invitations. The 2 colors of cardstock are fully customizable to suit your needs. The sheer organza ribbon will be the same color as the cardstock that outlines the text.

You can replace the pearls with rhinestones (clear or colored) if you'd prefer. The text can be printed on white or off-white cardstock and the font/wording is also customizable. White envelopes are included in your order.

Below are the details for placing an order. If you have any questions please do not hesitate to ask.

PLACING AN ORDER:

1. Please do not purchase this listing; instead, contact me with the number of invitations you need and I will create a “custom” listing for you.

2. Shipping depends on the quantity you order, so please convo me for a quote.

3. After placing your order please provide me with the shower information and your color choices.

4. Once I receive confirmation that the order was placed I will get started on creating your initial design proof (1-2 days). I will send it to you via email and allow you to make as many changes/corrections as needed. I will NOT print the invitation info until I receive your approval.

**Please keep in mind that YOU are responsible for ensuring that there are no mistakes on your proof prior to printing. I am a good proofreader, but please review the proof very carefully so that you are happy with your order.

5. Expect your invitations to ship in about a week from purchase. (This time may vary slightly depending on the size of your order).


GUARANTEE
I am extremely detail-oriented and back up my work 100%. If for any reason you are not completely satisfied I will make it right (but I'm sure you will LOVE your item)!

name: Wedding Photo Decor Frame
description:
This classy custom-designed 8" x 10" framed artwork is a perfect wedding or bridal shower gift. This particular design fits one 5" x 5" photo, but I can change the size if requested.

I'd love to design a photo frame around your wedding theme and/or colors. 

Once you order, send me a photo or let me know which colors to use and I'll work with you to find the perfect color and pattern combination for your wedding.

The "love" letters are on dimensional chipboard. It can say anything you'd like, such as a last name, date, or anything you can dream up (as long as it fits).

I can also rotate horizontally, and can use a larger frame for an additional fee. (Contact me for a quote.)

I look forward to working with you!
